### 2. Add the War Plugin (Recommended)
While Maven often handles this automatically, it is best practice to ensure the `maven-war-plugin` is included in your `build` section to ensure everything is packaged correctly for a web container (like Tomcat):

```xml
<build>
    <plugins>
        <plugin>
            <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
            <artifactId>maven-war-plugin</artifactId>
            <version>3.4.0</version>
        </plugin>
    </plugins>
</build>
